OL,3,CPlans to increase capacity of popular
OL,4,Cseaside festival approved
OL,6,FPlans to increase the capacity of
OL,7,FBoardmasters music festival at Newquay
OL,8,Fhave been approved by Cornwall
OL,9,Fcouncillors.
OL,11,FOrganisers had applied for permission
OL,12,Fto offer another 5,000 tickets this
OL,13,Fyear - bringing the total capacity to
OL,14,F58,000, including staff.
OL,16,FIn 2023 just over 48,000 tickets were
OL,17,Fsold and there were just under 5,000
OL,18,Fstaff. Last year Lorde, Liam
OL,19,FGallagher, and Florence and the
OL,20,FMachine topped the bill.
