OL,3,CPlans to increase capacity of popular
OL,4,Cseaside festival approved
OL,6,FAn online meeting of Cornwall
OL,7,FCouncil's licensing sub committee,
OL,8,Fwhich lasted five hours, heard
OL,9,Fconcerns over emergency evacuation and
OL,10,Ftraffic management.
OL,12,FThe lawyer representing Boardmasters
OL,13,Fat the meeting, Matthew Phipps, said:
OL,14,F"We are constantly looking to learn
OL,15,Fand improve.
OL,17,F"But I am bound to make the point that
OL,18,Fcongestion as an example, delays on
OL,19,Fthe road network, is not public
OL,20,Fnuisance."
