OL,3,CPlans to increase capacity of popular
OL,4,Cseaside festival approved
OL,6,FThe committee agreed the application
OL,7,Fto increase capacity, a move which has
OL,8,Fbeen welcomed by Newquay BID, which
OL,9,Frepresents businesses in the town.
OL,11,FMark Warren, from Newquay BID, said:
OL,12,F"For Newquay it brings around #40m of
OL,13,Fadditional revenue.
OL,15,F"Now that's not necessarily to the
OL,16,Fbusinesses but it's to the
OL,17,Ftradespeople that come and all the
OL,18,Fpeople that work at Boardmasters
OL,19,Fthrough the season.
