OL,6,F"And there's a lot of pre-work that
OL,7,Fgoes on and a lot of after-work that
OL,8,Fgoes on for the festival so it's a
OL,9,Fhuge part of the revenue that comes
OL,10,Finto Cornwall and Newquay."
OL,12,FAndrew Topham, Boardmasters CEO and
OL,13,FFestival Organiser, said: "We're
OL,14,Fdelighted that Cornwall Council has
OL,15,Fgranted us permission to expand
OL,16,FBoardmasters to a new total capacity
OL,17,Fof 58,000 from this summer.
